body:
All others tried to somehow Make Darius a vital part of the team comp, C9 was the first to actually use him how hes brokenly OP: as an addition that basicly says &quot;You either use all you have to stop Darius solo-raping you, but then our mid and ADC will kill you cause you just blew EVERYTHING to stop Darius, or you attack our ADC and Mid, but then you wont have anything to stop Darius from putting his axe so deep in your ass, you cut your tongue on the blade.&quot;

Cause thats whats actually broken on the Juggernauts, the amount of Skills you need to stop them. 
GG C9, cheap champ, but for being the first ones to get it, you deserved to win.
